Dialogue: The head of the Statue of Liberty: There is a new mark on the face… it reads "Lie". A coup d'etat occurred to rid of the corruption and lies.
The tablet of the Statue of Liberty: Date reads 04/04/2044… The new day of independence. Another war lasting 15 years, United States of America was finally freed from their shackles.
The torch of the Statue of Liberty: The fire is no longer present. The light guiding society was lost and only darkness remained.
The head of the Sphinx: Partially survived due to the gold coating. It appears it was coated as protection from something.
The hands of the Sphinx: Severally broken and cracks. It appears that natural disasters were the cause of the Sphinx destruction.
The rear of the Sphinx: The rear has also been covered in gold. Nothing much too see here…
There are traces of someone investigating this piece approximately 10 years ago.
